# --- Added for Frontend Workspace ---

# Environment Files (Broadened to catch .env.local)
**/.env*

# Local Logs, Diagnostics, and Temp Files
**/*.log
**/*.txt
**/.tmp_*
**/eslint-report.json

# Test Directories and Configs
**/e2e/
**/jest.config.js
**/jest.setup.js

# Code Formatters & Linters
**/.prettier*
**/eslint.config.js
**/lint.json

# Markdown documentation (not needed in container)
**/*.md

# Loose root design/temp assets
/png.png
/controller_frontend_map_full.json